      "description": "Good, well-kept older car that presents nicely and should make a solid driver for someone looking for a clean example without paying mint-condition money. The body and paint show well overall, though you should still expect some normal age-related cosmetic wear and minor imperfections if you look closely. The interior is tidy and well cared for, and overall it gives the impression of a car that has been maintained rather than neglected. This is not a show car, but it is a respectable, attractive older vehicle you can enjoy and improve over time if you want.",
