      "description": "A well-kept, good-condition example that should appeal to buyers looking for a clean, usable car without paying top-tier money. The exterior presents nicely overall with a good shine and solid appearance, though a close look should reveal some normal cosmetic age and use rather than show-level perfection. The interior appears tidy and presentable, with the kind of light wear you\u2019d expect from a car that has been enjoyed but not neglected. Overall, this looks like a sound, honest driver that should make a buyer feel good about using and showing it, provided expectations are set for a nice car rather than a mint one.",
